Usage:

  bundle
  rake spec:unit

Example output:

  $ time rake spec:unit
  .............. etc.
  
  Finished in 0.10109 seconds
  1000 examples, 0 failures
  
  Real	0m0.596s
  User	0m0.518s
  Sys	0m0.075s

Good to know:

If you have a Guardfile and run guard with bundle exec, you might want to escape it when running non-rails specs. You can do this by clearing RUBYOPT.

    RUBYOPT='' rspec unit/...